main.name: Phouthasak Douanglee
main.bio: I am an athlete at heart with the passion for solid software engineer fundamentals. After graduating from the University of Toledo, I left the small city of Toledo, Ohio to pursue my career as a software developer in Columbus, Ohio. I was hired by JP Morgan Chase & Co. as a full stack software engineer. Here is where I am able to hone my development skills to produce high quality web applications. I am currently working on getting on my AWS Certified Developer - Associate Certification.
